events.name: Minnesota Timberwolves at New York Knicks

headlines.description: — This was always Jacqueline Cruz-Towns' favorite game, when her family could gather to watch her son play the New York Knicks at Madison Square Garden.
headlines.shortLinkText: Towns' three-point play helps Wolves edge Knicks 112-110

events.name: Detroit Pistons at Golden State Warriors

headlines.description: — Klay Thompson found his shooting stroke and Warriors fans roared at every chance. Just like the old days.
headlines.shortLinkText: Splash Brothers Curry, Thompson lead Warriors past Pistons
